The use of deep learning techniques to learn vector embeddings of datasets is a key aspect of the paper, which suggests that it may also be relevant to the subfield of deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of string data, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper also discusses dataset search and schema matching tasks, which are topics that fall under the subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR).
